## Constraints humans care about

- **Safety:** Full passthrough preferred; avoid full-screen opaque overlays in real movement.  
- **Fork-friendly:** Avoid giant proprietary blobs; document Meta SDK import path.  
- **Small PRs:** Per user preference, avoid drive-by refactors.  

